body_html:
I did a bit of digging into this, and the problem is that cwise_op_abs.cc is not included in https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/tf_cc_files.txt

This is generated from the Bazel build files, so I have a proper fix in review, but in the short term you should just be able to add tensorflow/core/kernels/cwise_op_abs.cc to that file locally, and re-run compile_ios_tensorflow.sh.
